quote.summary: Jiangxi Bank Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in banking businesses and related financial services. The Company operates four segments. Corporate Banking segment provides financial products and services to corporations, government agencies and financial institutions, including corporate loans and advances, trade financing and deposit taking activities, agency services, consulting and advisory services, remittance and settlement services and guarantee services. Retail Banking And Credit Card segment provides financial products and services to retail customers, including personal loans and deposit taking activities, bank card business, personal wealth management services and remittance services. Financial Markets Business segment covers financial markets business operations, including inter-bank money market transactions, repurchases transactions and investments. The Others segment includes other related comprehensive banking businesses.
